values:
To all my JB's:&nbsp;Happy Father's Day to you, your DC, your DH/DP, your dads, friends, and&nbsp; anyone else&nbsp;you consider&nbsp;"dad" in your kiddos lives.&nbsp;

And of course, to all the solo moms&nbsp;--&nbsp; Happy Father's Day to you all - you are &nbsp;mom, dad, friend, parent, and number one love to the most important person on this planet. Your child(ren).

Enjoy your day.

Gals - I'm in need of new antivirus software on my laptop - set to expire in a day or two. The free trial is up. Norton is what was on my laptop when I bought it but at $50 for a renewal that seems a bit high.

I'm currently googling&nbsp;antiviral software but&nbsp;I'm not real well&nbsp;versed in this stuff.

Any recos?&nbsp;
